# Validate README
https://pbizopoulos.github.io/validate-readme

# Requirements
POSIX Utilities
Git
Docker

# Download
git clone https://github.com/pbizopoulos/validate-readme
cd validate-readme/

# Development
cd docs/ && make clean check all && cd ..
cd python/python/ && make clean check all && cd ../..
cd python/ && make clean check all && cd ..

# Staging
cd docs/ && make DEBUG=0

# Installation
pip install https://github.com/pbizopoulos/validate-readme/tarball/main#subdirectory=python

# Usage
validate_readme README

